  entryId: wolf_gray
  commonName: Gray Wolf
  scientificName: Canis lupus
  icon: {fileID: 2800000, guid: a6d9de680f8f0924fb51d8bea1901024, type: 3}
  category: Mammal
  habitat: Dense forest
  height: 0.80 m
  weight: 45 - 55 kg
  diet: Carnivore
  rarity: Uncommon
  shortDescription: A large predator that anchors the forest ecosystem and is usually sensed before it is seen.
  behaviorNotes: Wolves move with purpose, often staying to the edge of sight and traveling in packs when the scene calls for it.
  observationTips: Listen for movement and look for stronger silhouettes in the distance. This entry works well as a later-game discovery.
  funFact: A wolf's howl can be heard up to 10 kilometers away.
  facts:
  - The wolf asset gives the Pokedex a larger and more dramatic animal example.
  - Use this entry to introduce a higher-rarity discovery tier.
  - Wolves help sell the fantasy of a living wilderness rather than a static scene.
